{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

Template intended to force [[Nastaʿlīq script]] fonts if installed:
* "Urdu Typesetting" -- Proprietary Microsoft font that is available on Windows 8 and Windows 8.1.
* IranNastaliq
** [https://web.archive.org/web/20120207153145/http://www.scict.ir/Portal/File/ShowFile.aspx?ID=a0d2b2c1-44fd-4377-98ff-71b1b1aef828 Archived on the Wayback Machine], [https://www.yjc.ir/fa/news/4555441/%D8%A2%D8%AE%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AE%D9%87-%D9%81%D9%88%D9%86%D8%AA-%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%82-%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AF yjc], [http://www.parsilatex.com/joomla/index.php/remository/Fonts/%D9%81%D9%88%D9%86%D8%AA-%D8%AE%D9%88%D8%B4%D9%86%D9%88%DB%8C%D8%B3%DB%8C-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%82-(Iran-Nastaliq-Font)/ parsilatex] (rest of the links has become outdated and broken)
