* Nafees Nastaleeq [http://www.cle.org.pk/software/localization/Fonts/nafeesNastaleeq.html] > [https://www.cle.org.pk/Downloads/localization/fonts/NafeesNastaleeq/Nafees_Nastaleeq_v1.02.zip]
* Pak Nastaleeq [https://web.archive.org/web/20100701104014/http://www.nlauit.gov.pk/downloads.htm]
* Noto Nastaliq Urdu [https://noto-website-2.storage.googleapis.com/pkgs/NotoNastaliqUrdu-unhinted.zip] [https://github.com/googlei18n/noto-fonts/tree/master/phaseIII_only/unhinted/ttf/NotoNastaliqUrdu]
